name: Madisyn Robb
title: Secretary
description: Madisyn Robb is a freshman at Central Michigan University, where she serves as one of the Membership and Data Organizer for the Campus Democrats. Pursuing a major in History with a minor in Spanish, Madisyn aspires to become a history teacher. In addition to her political involvement, she plays trombone in the CMU Marching Band and is a member of the Rho Delta chapter of the Phi Mu sorority. Madisyn enjoys watching football and baseball games with her friends in her free time, as well as reading and writing.
